{"id":232934927,"title":"#詢問馬祖南竿住宿/交通選擇","content":"版上大大們好\n如果有人去過南竿\n可以推薦當時住的民宿嗎\n我在考慮要住港口旁還是住在鐵堡/北海坑道那\n因為想說晚上看藍眼淚是夜路\n民宿就在附近會不會比較好？\n還是應該住在港口鬧區？\n/\n另外五月底霧季去是不是飛機很容易不飛呀\n打算船去機回\n假期有限想玩到最後一刻\n但很怕卡在飛機飛不了\n網上各種偏方都看了（XD\n像是說選中午附近飛因為高溫霧氣會散一點😂\n有人去馬祖遇到停飛滯留的嗎🥺\n歡迎給我打氣或打預防針😂\n（有人為了這個去保旅遊不便險的嗎）\n\n謝謝大大們的分享\n祝大家旅途都平安順利\n\n最後附張藍眼淚，希望能看到！\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f1fb47bf-91f5-4cfa-8dd3-2cb462153de7/full.jpeg","excerpt":"版上大大們好，如果有人去過南竿，可以推薦當時住的民宿嗎，我在考慮要住港口旁還是住在鐵堡/北海坑道那，因為想說晚上看藍眼淚是夜路，民宿就在附近會不會比較好？還是應該住在港口鬧區？/，另外五月底霧季去是不","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"a255fb97-4199-4bd0-9b28-1ec2c0d2f382","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-21T18:23:43.255Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-21T18:23:43.255Z","commentCount":9,"likeCount":3,"tags":[],"topics":["住宿","交通","馬祖","南竿"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"旅遊","forumAlias":"travel","school":"🤓","department":"nozomi0414","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":3}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f1fb47bf-91f5-4cfa-8dd3-2cb462153de7/full.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"d937e7ca-7792-4f5d-a4d3-cbaa2e7058c6","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f1fb47bf-91f5-4cfa-8dd3-2cb462153de7/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f1fb47bf-91f5-4cfa-8dd3-2cb462153de7/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f1fb47bf-91f5-4cfa-8dd3-2cb462153de7/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":[],"createdAt":"2020-01-21T18:23:43.255Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-21T18:23:43.255Z","width":640,"height":457},{"id":"d937e7ca-7792-4f5d-a4d3-cbaa2e7058c6","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/f1fb47bf-91f5-4cfa-8dd3-2cb462153de7/full